{
  "id": "RAW_730bcac6",
  "title": "M5 款 MacBook Pro 深度体验：常规升级之下，是对「未来」的布局……",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247599776&idx=1&sn=0be446a6cd690edc6bf4f3dc1f9b74e6",
  "date": "2025-11-10 04:22:00",
  "author": "少数派",
  "siteName": "少数派",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100116102\" data-ratio=\"0.6657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d6806ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqscEIOsia8A1QAAYzSWFw51YA8c6Z2icJ3Zkr8aiar7t6dheWANCc1R1yWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">外观和配置：基本都没变</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">M5 款 MacBook Pro 是该系列的一次常规升级，常规到除了更新了 M5 芯片之外，其它配置基本都没变。为了节约你</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">的阅读时间，我会在本节简要描述一下新老款之间相同的部分。如果你想更详细地了解基础款 MacBook Pro，可以搭配阅读 M4 版 MacBook Pro 的体验文章。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&amp;mid=2247583607&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cdaa7f1013753ba5f3cebbde45e56d1b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"「低配」不低能：2024 款 MacBook Pro 快速体验\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「低配」不低能：2024 款 MacBook Pro 快速体验</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">首先，新老款的外观没有任何变化，从漆面质感到键盘手感都很一致，甚至连重量也完全相同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100116103\" data-ratio=\"0.33240740740740743\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=424fec6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqshrIF33JTcuZVMYSHawyxaticBH71iaUEN7EKmbRLmIJFibF4x708pnvKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">其次，基础款 Apple silicon 的纸面参数看起来也变化不大，M4 和 M5 都拥有十核中央处理器（CPU）、十核图形处理器（GPU）和十六核神经网络引擎（NPU），最高支援 32GB 内存。在此基础上，M5 的内存带宽升级到了 153GB/s，并可选最高 4TB 的存储空间（M4 是 2TB）。另外，Apple 大幅提升了 M5 的 NPU 性能，具体区别会在下文对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116104\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7129629629629629\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36abd6a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsoblGCI0EqEW2DV7yVAe0smCibZA8H8h1mcdAtibXYjuUDqOHVgkEXeXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">M5（左）和 M4 芯片的核心参数对比，图片截取自 Apple</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116105\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=612af336&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsD7nA45ZKknpeHTib5eSVkgqSSy014Cqtxh1MdcMrPBG4L20ecZOxTBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">NPU 的性能提升是本代 Apple silicon 的最大亮点，图片截取自 Apple</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">再其次，新老两代的续航能力也没有区别，都是典型的 Apple silicon 式体验——即使高频使用，也只需要一天一充。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100115530\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2000\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71c64bc4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Foylw20gGnRh2Bbibboz1kiatbtur5x5BxfbsxuIALOMib1iaPYW8Q6NfJJP91PUoYW8licytbmutGjgiaWiaoawvLmLAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最后，我想额外多聊两句纳米纹理屏。在使用上一代 MacBook Pro 的时候，我觉得纳米纹理屏是个不太适合多数用户的选择，因为它会一定程度上牺牲萤幕的显示效果——你花了 Pro 的钱买了一块色准、亮度都很棒的 Liquid 视网膜 XDR 显示屏，却还要额外再花钱削弱它的显示效果，听起来有点得不偿失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116106\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c75fd96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsogGujcUh98VibO787Ow19tozNp0wCCR0rYuY8xribiac6tF5APuB7Gpgw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">即使是在户外，配备了纳米纹理屏的 MacBook 也能清晰地显示任何内容</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">但在那之后，我开始留意身边的工作和生活环境，发现各种奇奇怪怪的光源干扰其实还挺多。特别是各种办公场所很少考虑到电子设备的萤幕反光问题，大量使用高亮度的点光源而非平面光，所以「一打开电脑，满屏都是眩光点」的状况非常严重。在这样的环境里，纳米纹理萤幕带来的抗反射效果就显得尤为实用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">所以，我的观点变了：如果你有意购买新机，我建议你可以先观察一下自己高频使用电脑的环境。如果光源控制得不好，且你又需要长期使用笔记本的自带萤幕，那纳米纹理屏应上尽上。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">性能：NPU 的大进化</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先简单概括一句：目前的主流测试结果都认为，M5 款 MacBook Pro 相较前代在 CPU 部分小幅提升，GPU 性能提升了 20% 到 30%，NPU 性能则大幅提升。我的结论也基本一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">而在测试方法上，我依然刻意排除了跑分工具，选取了几个我自己日常高频使用且确实有代表性的 app，来对比 M4 和 M5 在真实使用环境里的性能差异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先从播客剪辑工具《Reaper》开始。我选择了投资人 Naval 知名的长播客《How to Get Rich》作为音源，并截取了播客的前一小时，外挂一个智能音频优化插件 dxRevive Pro，输出为 .mp3 格式的音频文件。音频渲染主要考验 CPU 的能力，而 dxRevive Pro 又是个极其吃性能的插件，渲染完毕后，M4 的用时为 00:03:43，而 M5 则为 00:03:30，M5 略胜一筹。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116107\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.912962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bfca8f48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsADkPj4etuz2cI1JMZMqQknTBicslUxDibaG2Z8VjZa2Lk4WGOCy3v0DQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">使用《Reaper》渲染音频</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第二项是使用知名图片处理工具《Pixelmator》内建的超分功能（Super Upscale），把一张 iPhone 16 Pro 拍摄的 24MP 照片分辨率提升一倍。这个功能会用到机器学习算法，主要依赖 NPU 的性能。M4 用时 00:00:14，而 M5 则为 00:00:12，由于只超分一张照片，所以两者的差距不算明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116108\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.674074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=610da1d4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsChgQKzibtLT2D0hIia9p3cHQicKv6XRrSX5JTTmwzLtGYjIXben8exyzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">使用《Pixelmator》超分图片，最终成片分辨率是 11424×8568</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">接下来的测试负载开始加重，M5 在 GPU 和 NPU 上的性能优势也逐渐显露。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第三项是使用《Mac Whisper》内建的「Small」模型将一段英文 YouTube 影片转成文字，这个项目主要考验 NPU，是 Apple silicon 非常擅长的场景。原片大约十一分钟，总字符数（characters）超过了九千个。M4 用时 00:00:42，而 M5 则用时 00:00:31，一分钟内的转制任务就能拉开十秒钟的差距，M5 在这个项目里领先得很明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116109\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df963fff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsm7XRMPBpX8kF6WAE47lAkHr8RHmOXNCu9xHNvwK8HKmD48xia4XrAdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">使用《Mac Whisper》将音频转为文字</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第四项是使用《Topaz Photo》（原名为《Topaz Photo AI》）自动优化照片，这款工具主要考验 GPU 性能，同时，因为它调用了本地模型，所以也会用到 NPU 的能力。我分别找了风景、油画、明星肖像和卡通形象四个类型的照片各五张，让 app 以自动模式（Auto Pilot）将它们批量优化和导出。M4 用时 00:01:25，而 M5 则用时 00:01:17。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116110\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5972222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4d538d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsoJib2LVS3fWZvDFvbpOpbFfmvWoYU9DtvC5dVO10UJM9T1pMgvoiazBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">使用《Topaz Photo》优化照片</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最后一项是使用《DaVinci Resolve》挂载 Dehancer 胶片模拟插件，为一段时长三分钟、4K 60p、使用 iPhone 17 Pro 拍摄、Open Gate 模式、ProRes RAW 格式的影片调色，开启色彩模拟、噪点模拟和光晕模拟功能，导出为 H265 的高码率 4K 60p 影片。这是个重载任务，Dehancer 非常吃显存和 GPU 性能，ProRes RAW 的编解码也是大活，两台电脑都用了超过原片数倍的时长才完成了任务。最终，M4 耗时 00:19:40，而 M5 仅为 00:14:57，在这项对 CPU 和 GPU 的综合考验里，M5 也更完整地展现了它对 M4 的优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116111\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=464c5cb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqs9T8mUWEiaBDcXibY1AxpfS8TVT6dMxZfsC10DoBontMXuFq0vRMmP13Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">对非 Pro 和 Max 级别的芯片来说，搞 ProRes RAW 还是有点吃力</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">除了芯片性能，有媒体说 M5 款 MacBook Pro 的固态硬盘读写速度均有大幅提升。我测试之后发现所言非虚，读写速度都能稳定跑到 6000MB/s 以上，相当夸张。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116112\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0314814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5db186b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsKPydU4CR8sGrSjian2hEJhGv7ia4xm8lMad7yRtgPIMSVZA2jRZVROVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">M5 款 MacBook Pro 的 SSD 测速截图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">总体而言，虽然 M5 是一块基础款芯片，但它依然展现了自己「Pro」的一面。如果不运行大型任务，日常的码字、剪片、编程、修图等工作它全都应付得来。更重要的是，在 AI 和大模型的发展如火如荼的当下，M5 芯片无疑昭示了 Apple 的新野心——在这个领域，Apple silicon 将大有可为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116113\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e952e153&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsiaUS6icibkXNzNQibLwbGpsE6HkddYawmWvlF4m2O40fKIHPvzpxhdtXkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">AI 性能已经成了新款 MacBook 的重要宣传点，图片截取自 Apple</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">选购建议</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「基础款 MacBook Pro 到底是卖给谁的」，这个问题我想过很久。后来我发现，最不应该纠结这个问题的人就是我，因为我就是初代基础款的 MacBook Pro 用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116114\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9b8055f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsjweWedzF594PhGwzIibKZFSk7iaoxwh16Xxb4wBiag1C6Y5iabVT2FiasDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">——有这么一群人，他们对性能的需求并不高，MacBook Air 就能满足。但他们也想拥有观感更好的萤幕，想拥有立体声扬声器，想拥有录音棚级麦克风阵列，想拥有独立的 HDMI 接口和 SD 卡槽，甚至偶尔也会搞搞吃性能的项目。对于他们来说，基础款 MacBook Pro 才是更适合自己的选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116115\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.33240740740740743\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c6b6794&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqs2sicv0AeANT896t2oPoyEZMV1NIgVTLIhYKfO6SNepoWk1DptpHQoDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">另一个目标群体是还在使用 Intel 版 Mac 的用户。我曾经以为这样的遗老遗少数量并不多，但直到我发现身边也有这样的朋友，才意识到自己过于想当然了。在 Steam 平台的最新统计中，使用 Intel 版 Mac 的玩家超过了 15%。而有报道称，有超过 25% 的音频工作者还在使用 Intel 版 Mac。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我还记得自己从 15 英寸的顶配 Intel 版 MacBook Pro 换成 M1 版本时的心情，那是一种「他妈的我为什么要为这个破玩意花三万块」的震撼。M5 确实是基础款，但如果对比几年前的老芯片，它只会赢得一骑绝尘。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116116\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80ae5230&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjqMXybHUfA9LlXvibw5iajqsbfrhrytqJWn4tVWdzyaqHaAs5pEkA1Hm1icwfhvb79DlFOMjcOmSvUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">M5 款 MacBook Pro，你觉得怎么样？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/103563?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspai.com/post/103563?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：</span><span leaf=\"\">张奕源Nick</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "M5 款 MacBook Pro 常规升级，NPU 性能显著提升，预示 Apple 在 AI 领域的未来布局。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "M5 款 MacBook Pro 常规升级，NPU 性能显著提升，预示 Apple 在 AI 领域的未来布局。",
  "summary": "本文深度体验了 M5 款 MacBook Pro，指出其在外观和大部分配置上与前代 M4 基本无异，核心亮点在于 NPU 性能的大幅跃升和 GPU 的显著增强。作者通过实际应用场景测试（如音频剪辑、图片超分、语音转文字、批量修图、视频调色）对比 M4 和 M5 的性能差异，证实了 M5 在 AI 相关任务上的优势。同时，文章也探讨了纳米纹理屏的实用价值和 M5 MacBook Pro 的目标用户群体，包括对 MacBook Air 性能不满足但又不需要 Pro/Max 芯片的用户，以及从 Intel Mac 升级的用户。作者强调 M5 芯片的强大 NPU 性能是 Apple 在 AI 时代的重要战略布局。",
